9/04/19/cover-me-long-tall-sally/", "url_meta": {"origin": 15837, "position": 4}, "title": "Cover Me: Long Tall Sally", "author": "Ken", "date": "April 19, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "Lots of times with lots of people: \"Long Tall Sally\" is tried and true when Bruce joins fellow musicians for an impromptu jam. Check out some of his best performances inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/little-richard-long-tall-sally-big.jpg?fit=620%2C627&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/little-richard-long-tall-sally-big.jpg?fit=620%2C627&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/little-richard-long-tall-sally-big.jpg?fit=620%2C627&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 9730, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/05/08/cover-me-the-wanderer/", "url_meta": {"origin": 15837, "position": 5}, "title": "Cover Me: The Wanderer", "author": "Ken", "date": "May 8, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce played Dion's \"The Wanderer\" three times with its original artist, long before he took a run at it with the E Street Band. Watch and listen to great performances across three decades.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/dion_the-wanderer-the-majesticoriginal-us.-picture-_1.jpg?fit=600%2C596&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/dion_the-wanderer-the-majesticoriginal-us.-picture-_1.jpg?fit=